        "deck": "Volume 1.",
        "description": "<p>This series is the very first volume of The Incredible Hulk where a mishap with a gamma bomb changed <a href=\"/hulk/4005-2267/\" data-ref-id=\"4005-2267\"> Dr. Bruce Banner's</a> life and the <a href=\"/marvel/4010-31/\" data-ref-id=\"4010-31\"> Marvel</a> Universe forever. In the first issue, the Hulk was grey, but due to ink-problems that made it difficult to have a grey character on every page, he was made green in the following issues. The series lasted only 6 issues, but the Hulk's adventures continued in <a href=\"/tales-to-astonish/4050-2008/\" data-ref-id=\"4050-2008\">Tales To Astonish</a> issue 59 and on some years later.</p><h4>Collected Editions</h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/incredible-hulk-epic-collection-man-or-monster/4050-91103/\" data-ref-id=\"4050-91103\">Incredible Hulk Epic Collection: Man or Monster?</a></li><li><a href=\"/kingsize-kirby/4050-83141/\" data-ref-id=\"4050-83141\">King-Size Kirby</a> (#3)</li><li><a href=\"/marvel-masterworks-the-incredible-hulk/4050-35210/\" data-ref-id=\"4050-35210\">Marvel Masterworks: Incredible Hulk</a>, Vol. 1</li></ul><h4>Non-U.S. Collected Editions</h4><ul><li><a href=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/coleccionable-marvel-heroes-13-hulk-los-perros-de-/4000-612218/\">Coleccionable Marvel Héroes: Hulk: Los perros de la guerra</a> (#1) (Spanish)</li><li><a href=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/kingsize-kirby/4050-104017/\" data-ref-id=\"4050-104017\">Marvel Gold. El Increíble Hulk</a> (#1-6) (Spanish)</li><li><a href=\"https://comicvine.gamespot.com/kingsize-kirby/4050-104017/\" data-ref-id=\"4050-104017\">King-Size Kirby</a><span> (#3) (Spanish)</span></li></ul>",
